%N A394712 Decimal expansion of the asymptotic probability that two nonsquarefree numbers selected independently at random are coprime.
%F A394712 Equals (6/Pi^2 - 2 * Product_{p prime} (1 - 2/p^2 + 1/p^3) + Product_{p prime} (1 - 3/p^2 + 2/p^3)) / (1 - 6/Pi^2)^2 = (A059956 - 2 * A065464 + A065473) / A229099^2.
%F A394712 Equals A394711 / A229099^2.
%e A394712 0.2483426456381285816837884662384461625097516943278706...
%o A394712 (PARI) (6/Pi^2 - 2 * prodeulerrat(1 - 2/p^2 + 1/p^3) + prodeulerrat(1 - 3/p^2 + 2/p^3)) / (1 - 6/Pi^2)^2
%Y A394712 Cf. A013929, A059956, A065464, A065473, A229099, A394711.
